pageContext.claim: “Most of the RINOs I beat, because you know, they were all representing one of the 17. Because we had 18 running. But they were, who, most of 'em, I get along with. Some of them, I don't like. I could tell you the good ones and the bad ones. But I beat all of these guys.”
pageContext.analysis: No, there were 17 people who sought the GOP nomination, including former Virginia governor Jim Gilmore.
